<title>USA: CompuServe names Softbank ad agent.</title>
<headline>CompuServe names Softbank ad agent.</headline>
<dateline>COLUMBUS, Ohio 1997-01-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>CompuServe Corp said Tuesday it has selected Softbank Internative Marketing Inc as the exclusive advertising sales agent for its online services.</p>
<p>CompuServe said its alliance with Softbank is expected to allow it to capture a &quot;significant share&quot; of this growing source of online revenue.</p>
<p>As part of the deal, advertisers will be able to choose to run advertisements across numerous CompuServe products and services, and target them at members of specific audiences who are tapped into CompuServe.  Softbank Interactive Marketing is a United States unit of Japan-based Softbank Co.</p>
